_sText:
Well i do believe i have fixed all the bugs from the first version.
the only thing i know i didn't fix was the entrance to the cave.
there's a bunch of custom things in this.
there is still a console error for some tree leaves i have no idea how to fix that or why its showing up, the leaves work just fine in game.
i have added clouds to the map 
and have changed the ground texture to one with grass details.
i have also changed the water textures and the roof and stair textures.
zzdd has optimized it a lot better than i did in the first version i get about 20 - 40 more fps all over the map.
I may have a custom nav file for this coming soon.
have fun and thanks for downloading
